  "tips": [
    {
      "type": "lead",
      "text": "Last row on the map: the bottom one. We start with the strong fingers, like always. Index handles V M B N, middle grabs C. This is the row people fumble most, so we slow it down and lock it in."
    },
    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "The bottom row sits below home, so you curl your fingers down to reach it, not stretch out. V and B are left index, M and N are right index, C is left middle. Tap, then snap straight back to home. No need to look - feel for it."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "👇",
      "title": "Curl, don't slide",
      "text": "Don't drag your whole hand down. Just curl the one finger you need and let the rest stay parked on home. The faster you bounce back, the less you get lost."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "v v v v v m m m m m v m v m v m v m v m",
      "finger": "blue",
      "title": "Index: V and M",
      "hint": "V is left index curling down, M is right index. Alternate clean, space after each."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "b b b b b n n n n n b n b n b n b n b n",
      "finger": "blue",
      "title": "Index: B and N",
      "hint": "B left index, N right index, both on the bottom row. Curl down and pop back."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c c",
      "finger": "green",
      "title": "Middle: C",
      "hint": "C is your left middle finger curling down. Only this finger moves - rest stay home."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Bottom row is online. Now we cash it in on real words - the kind with V, M, B, N, C all mixed in. Read the whole word first, then type it smooth. Speed is not the goal yet, clean is."
    },
